      • getDiscipline

        public String getDiscipline()
        Discipline, to which the Revit parameter represented by this object belongs. Only relevant in case if there is more than one types with the same name (e.g. piping, HVAC and structural Velocity). Six sensible values can be applied: Common, Electrical, Energy, HVAC, Piping and Structural. (Required)
